node.text:
Sound 🔊 on for the full Tennessee Knockout with a dash of: “These rocks are slipperier than an otter’s pocket.” 

Here’s the #FIM Hard Enduro World Championship round @ this weekend’s Tennessee Knockout with a mild to ROWDY lap course preview from none other than @paulboltsenduro! 

Keep it dialed for the full TKO experience on Red Bull TV with the 🔗 in bio.

#enduro #hardenduro #POV #Struggle #Challenge #Yew #RedBullMotorsports
